                        }
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="align-items-center justify-content-end">
    <section class="ftco-appointment ftco-section ftco-no-pt ftco-no-pb">
        <div class="align-items-center justify-content-end">
            <div class="overlay"></div>
            <div class="container">
                <div class="row d-md-flex justify-content-center">
                    <div class="col-md-12">
                        <div class="wrap-appointment d-md-flex">
                            <div class="col-md-4 bg-white text-center p-5">
                                <div class="desc border-bottom pb-4">
                                    <h2>Business Hours</h2>
                                    <div class="opening-hours">
                                        <h4>Opening Days:</h4>
                                        <p class="pl-3">
                                            <span><strong>Monday – Friday:</strong> 9am to 20 pm</span>
                                            <span><strong>Saturday :</strong> 9am to 17 pm</span>
                                        </p>
                                        <h4>Vacations:</h4>
                                        <p class="pl-3">
                                            <span>All Sunday Days</span>
                                            <span>All Official Holidays</span>
                                        </p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="desc pt-4 ">
                                    <h3 class="heading">For Emergency Cases</h3>
                                    <span class="phone">(+01) 123 456 7890</span>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</div>
<section class="ftco-section">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center pb-5 mb-3">
            <div class="col-md-7 heading-section text-center ftco-animate">
                <h2>Speciality of our Doctors</h2>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-4 services ftco-animate">
                <div class="d-block d-flex">
                    <div class="icon d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center">
                        <span class="flaticon-chiropractic"></span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="media-body pl-3">
                        <h3 class="heading">Cardiologist</h3>
                        <p>We deal with the disorders of the heart as well as some parts of the Circulatory System.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="d-block d-flex">
                    <div class="icon d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center">
                        <span class="flaticon-acupuncture"></span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="media-body pl-3">
                        <h3 class="heading">Dentist</h3>
                        <p>We study, diagnos, prevent, and treat diseases, disorders, and conditions of the Oral Cavity.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4 services ftco-animate">
                <div class="d-block d-flex">
                    <div class="icon d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center">
                        <span class="flaticon-electrotherapy"></span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="media-body pl-3">
                        <h3 class="heading">ENT Specialist</h3>
                        <p>We deal with the surgical and medical management of conditions of the head and neck.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="d-block d-flex">
                    <div class="icon d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center">
                        <span class="flaticon-examination"></span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="media-body pl-3">
                        <h3 class="heading">Gynaecologist</h3>
                        <p>We deal with the health of the female reproductive system (vagina, uterus, and ovaries).</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col-md-4 services ftco-animate">
                <div class="d-block d-flex">
                    <div class="icon d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center">
                        <span class="flaticon-lymph-nodes"></span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="media-body pl-3">
                        <h3 class="heading">Radiologist</h3>
                        <p>We diagnose and treat diseases within the bodies of animals, including humans.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="d-block d-flex">
                    <div class="icon d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center">
                        <span class="flaticon-bone"></span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="media-body pl-3">
                        <h3 class="heading">Neurologist</h3>
                        <p>We diagnos and treat of all categories of conditions and disease involving the central and peripheral nervous systems.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>


